10:36.080 --> 10:37.840
But in some ways, it doesn't matter

10:37.920 --> 10:41.000
because it's a reality that people have to face.

10:41.080 --> 10:43.320
I think what's fascinating about the book of Revelation

10:43.400 --> 10:46.760
is that it's so spectacular.

10:46.840 --> 10:53.640
It's an extraordinary visualisation of a cataclysm.

10:53.720 --> 10:55.280
And it's really very elaborate.

10:55.360 --> 10:58.120
It's worth reading and trying to picture it in your mind,

10:58.200 --> 11:02.640
and you realise that you would need the most advanced computer graphics

11:02.720 --> 11:06.080
to realise it on a screen.

11:06.160 --> 11:10.600
I think it's partly that you need a spectacular prelude

11:10.680 --> 11:13.560
for the Kingdom of God to be plausible,

11:13.640 --> 11:15.400
because the terrible truth about the Kingdom of God

11:15.440 --> 11:17.400
is that it does sound quite dull.

11:18.480 --> 11:24.760
I mean, the reality about the saints and angels

11:24.840 --> 11:29.320
