45:00.240 --> 45:01.920
There's a couple of themes you developed.

45:02.000 --> 45:08.320
So you pointed out that it's often the reaction to a crisis

45:08.320 --> 45:09.840
that's worse than the crisis,

45:09.920 --> 45:12.880
and you pointed to the law of unintended consequences

45:12.960 --> 45:14.000
as the cause of that.

